response.overview: On December 2nd GCW presents C'Mon Dude live on FITE+ straight from The Webster in Hartford, CT. The event features the GCW World Title Match where Blake Christian defends his title against Alec Price.  Also in the lineup:  Jimmy Lloyd vs Sawyer Wreck Parrow w/ Charles Mason vs Richard Holliday w/ Hammerstone  Tony Deppen vs Jordan Oliver Mance Warner vs Jimmy Lloyd  Effy vs Santana Jackson LuFisto vs Unagi Sayaka  Tag Team Match Masha Slamovich & Rina Yamashita vs Miracle Generation (Dustin Waller & Kylon King)
response.title: GCW: C'Mon Dude
